as </LOCATION>, and seized documents they are still studying. They also filed notice of intention to seize the ranch and other property as the proceeds of illegal drug transactions. No criminal charges have been filed related to the operation of the Junior Ranch, but a federal grand jury convenes May 31 in <LOCATION> Muskogee </LOCATION>.
